CryptoMembership   is a Web3 alternative to Patreon, Discord subscriptions, and paid communities.

It allows creators or communities to:

Create paid memberships

Lock content / access behind crypto payments

Accept payment in ANY crypto

Use wallet-based access, not emails/passwords

It allows users to:

Join memberships easily

Pay using any crypto they already own

Prove membership via wallet (NFT-based)

